  "summary": "Expert assistant for chezmoi dotfiles management. Use when: \"add this file to chezmoi\", \"make this a template\", \"encrypt this secret\", \"apply on a new machine\", \"run script only once\", \"manage dotfiles across machines\".\n\nExamples:\n- user: \"Track my .zshrc with chezmoi\" → chezmoi add ~/.zshrc\n- user: \"Make my .gitconfig machine-specific\" → convert to .tmpl, use {{ .chezmoi.hostname }}\n- user: \"Run a script only on first apply\" → once_ prefix\n- user: \"Sync to a new laptop\" → chezmoi init --apply $GITHUB_USERNAME\n- user: \"Why isn't my file being applied?\" → diagnose source attribute, diff, doctor",
